    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the upright stones placed at the foot of graves, that is, over the feet of the interred body, generally shorter in height than the headstone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
